{"tid":676890,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"打完石膏有虛位可以郁","createTime":"2018-05-24T17:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T18:31:25.000Z","uid":16552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7581dcd852c79f9f5867e3853703b4c2b3387b2c","tid":676890,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"有冇熟骨科既巴絲係度?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前整親腳掌骨裂(# MT base)打左石膏, <br />\n由腳掌包到去小腿, 6星期後先覆診照x光拆石膏<br />\n而家過左一星期多d, 覺得石膏同腳踝有虛位<br />\n有時訓覺唔自覺郁到會痛醒, 平時唔郁就冇野<br />\n想問石膏入面有虛位到郁到腳腕是咪正常架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n憑感覺又唔係好清楚有幾多虛位,<br />\n少少plantar flexion, dorsal flexion, inversion eversion都得<br />\n做eversion同dorsal flexion就會痛, <br />\n我怕郁到個受傷位會影響條骨生番埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3f507e9ae45a560308bd48161bd08d84003a15","tid":676890,"uid":81308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:56:16.000Z","msg":"唔問個醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24b1d4b768608cb93fbf6432b0a0d048e0f9a66","tid":676890,"uid":16552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff3f507e9ae45a560308bd48161bd08d84003a15","tid":676890,"uid":81308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:56:16.000Z","msg":"唔問個醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:57:09.000Z","msg":"公院6星期後先有得覆診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030538363dd6fb39beb07fd91e027685e3487bbc","tid":676890,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:58:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔&gt;醫生"},{"pid":"189f08c8f884cb35c30ca42721bef58ad36decfc","tid":676890,"uid":39626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:01:05.000Z","msg